ğŸµ Input options: upload an audio clip, enter chords/genre, or provide song title/artist

ğŸ› Output: JSON with amp model + normalized knob values (gain, bass, mid, treble, presence, reverb)

ğŸ¤– AI core: rule-based predictor (MVP) + hooks for PyTorch models

ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» Feedback loop: collect user ratings to refine future predictions

â˜ï¸ Deploy-ready: Dockerized backend, frontend deployable on Vercel/Netlify, backend on Render/Cloud Run

ğŸ”— Extensible: support for exporting presets to popular amp sims (planned)

Tech Stack

Frontend: React + TypeScript + TailwindCSS

Backend: FastAPI (Python), librosa, optional PyTorch

Storage: S3 (or any object store), Postgres (Supabase recommended)

Infra: Docker, GitHub Actions (CI/CD), Vercel/Render/Cloud Run

Optional: Redis for job queueing, Hugging Face/Replicate for GPU inference
